OL,4,G1900FGPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,5,     GDr Sian Morris suspects that long-
OL,6,     Gterm patient Allan's recent
OL,7,     Gdramatic weight loss is a result
OL,8,     Gof his addiction to crack cocaine.
OL,9,G2000FCasualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,10,     GIt's another gruelling shift for
OL,11,     Gteam at Barnsley Hospital's
OL,12,     GCasualty Department. Juggling a
OL,13,     Gback-log of walk-in patients and
OL,14,     Ga constant stream of new
OL,15,     Gambulance emergencies.
OL,16,G2100FAmbulance: Code Red
OL,17,     GA 52-year-old man complains of
OL,18,     Gneck and shoulder pains after
OL,19,     Gbeing thrown off his motorbike,
OL,20,     Gand a 40-year-old epileptic woman
OL,21,     Ghas collapsed with a dangerously
OL,22,     Glow breathing rate.
