OL,4,G0200FCasualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,5,     GThe flow of patients at Barnsley
OL,6,     GCasualty is relentless, and today
OL,7,     Gstaff are put under even more
OL,8,     Gpressure by patients suffering
OL,9,     Gfrom the effects of drink or
OL,10,     Gdrugs.
OL,11,G0245FSkin A&E
OL,12,     GDr Adil Sheraz is called a magic
OL,13,     Gman after making a giant ear
OL,14,     Gkeloid disappear. A breakdancer
OL,15,     Gwants Dr Natalia Spierings to
OL,16,     Gremove head cysts that get in the
OL,17,     Gway of his head spins.
OL,18,G0335FFriends
OL,19,     GPhoebe is horrified when she is
OL,20,     Gpropositioned by Rachel's Italian
OL,21,     Gboyfriend. Meanwhile, Monica
OL,22,     Gstruggles with a surfeit of pasta.
